  • The data presented is based on AP ICET 2024 final seat allotment and confirmed student admissions.

  • Values marked as 0 indicate either:
    • No students joined in that category through ICET, or

  • Dropouts and spot admissions are not reflected in this data.
  • The data is provided only for information and reference, and does not guarantee admissions in the current or upcoming year.
  • While efforts have been made to ensure accuracy, we are not responsible for minor errors or omissions.

About Us

About Bhargav's Buzz

Welcome to Bhargav's Buzz – Your Trusted Education and Career Companion!

I'm Bhargav, the creator and voice behind Bhargav's Buzz. What started as a small initiative in December 2019 has now grown into a dynamic and supportive platform that helps thousands of students every year.

🌱 The Beginning

The channel was originally named BC2MS, a heartfelt combination of my close friends' names. It began on YouTube, during the early rise of student-centric social media content. My goal was simple – to support students by providing clear and reliable updates.

📈 The Growth

In 2020, during the peak of the COVID-19 pandemic, Bhargav's Buzz became a lifeline for many students. I shared timely updates about AP Intermediate, EAMCET, and other entrance exams, helping over 5,000+ students navigate uncertain times with confidence.

Recognizing the growing need, I rebranded the channel to Bhargav's Buzz, reflecting a more personal and professional identity.

📚 AP ICET & Beyond

In 2023, my focus shifted towards AP ICET updates and other Common Entrance Tests. Bhargav's Buzz quickly became a go-to hub for entrance exam aspirants looking for trustworthy, easy-to-understand information and timely updates.

Here, you'll find the most reliable and student-friendly updates available – all in one place.

👨‍💻 My Journey

Alongside managing the channel, I began pursuing my Master of Computer Applications (MCA) in 2023. Balancing my academics with content creation was challenging, but it taught me valuable lessons in time management and dedication. Today, I share updates not just on YouTube, but also via Instagram, WhatsApp Contacts, and our growing WhatsApp Community & Groups.

This ecosystem makes it easier to provide quick, bite-sized updates directly to students, wherever they are. Many members are now active followers, and their feedback continues to inspire and guide my work.

💡 Why Bhargav's Buzz?

  • Real-time Updates: AP ICET, TS ICET, EAMCET, and other entrance exams
  • Trusted by Thousands: A growing student community with a shared goal
  • Student-first Approach: Clear, concise, and timely information
  • Multi-platform Access: YouTube, Instagram, and WhatsApp Communities
  • Run by a Student, for Students

🔖 Tagline:

"Bhargav's Buzz – Where Every Student's Future Gets the Right Signal!"

Thank you for being part of this journey.

Nenu Mee MCA Bhargav, Repati Kosam. 🌟

Connect with me on LinkedIn: VENKATA BHARGAV VINJAMURU

Our Mission

At Bhargav's Buzz, we are committed to providing comprehensive guidance and support to students preparing for and navigating the AP ICET counseling process. Our goal is to empower students with accurate information, personalized advice, and a supportive community to help them make informed decisions about their academic and professional future.

Our Audience

We cater to students who have appeared for the AP ICET examination and are looking for guidance on college selection, course options, and career opportunities. Our resources are designed to help students at every stage of their journey, from exam preparation to final admission.
